explanation: This solution uses a single pass through the numbers from 1 to n to calculate the sum of digits for each number and store the count in an array. Then it iterates through the array to find the maximum count and the number of groups with this maximum count. The space complexity is O(1) because the size of the array is fixed and does not depend on the input n.

